server.model.players

Enum EquipmentListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<EquipmentListener>
      • server.model.players.EquipmentListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<EquipmentListener>

    public enum EquipmentListener
extends java.lang.Enum<EquipmentListener>
    The EquipmentListener(int) enumeration represents the slot values for when Equipping or Removing items from the slotId. The slotId values are numerically accurate, but correct for viewing the models when equipping the items, etc..
    Author:
    Dennis
